729
00:43:13.798 --> 00:43:17.658
And now these mutations are actually slightly different in terms of where they are,

730
00:43:17.678 --> 00:43:20.258
and I'll get into that in just a minute.

731
00:43:20.358 --> 00:43:24.198
So it's possible that the frequency of these types of mutations may vary

732
00:43:24.238 --> 00:43:24.618
from one

733
00:43:25.997 --> 00:43:26.938
inhibitor to the other.

734
00:43:27.958 --> 00:43:30.878
So let me get a little bit of detail into the structure here.

735
00:43:30.978 --> 00:43:34.818
This is a structure of minin. This is most of minin here,

736
00:43:35.258 --> 00:43:38.978
a bit of Ledgef, and just the very N-terminus of MLL here in

